name: Cake is Kate. Always has been 💫

content.html: It took me about 5 minutes to start locally running an open source Ruby project despite the fact that I never touched Ruby on Rails in the past & project itself didn’t have related docs. Now that’s what I call strong external community resources that are easy to find 👏
content.value:
It took me about 5 minutes to start locally running an open source Ruby project despite the fact that I never touched Ruby on Rails in the past & project itself didn’t have related docs.

Now that’s what I call strong external community resources that are easy to find 👏
